Package gov.tak.api.datamodels

Class AttributeSetDataModelSpi

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.tak.api.datamodels.AttributeSetDataModelSpi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataModelSpi<AttributeSet>
    public final class AttributeSetDataModelSpi
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataModelSpi<AttributeSet>
    Primitive (except boolean) accepting put()s will remove KVPs if given their Object type's MIN_VALUE. Object type-accepting put()s will remove KVPs is provided null.
